* Description

  This repository is for OmniROM (4.4.4) on Samsung Galaxy SIV Mini a.k.a Samsung Serranoltexx.
  It's still a work in progress.

* How To Build OmniROM (4.4.4) for Samsung Serranoltexx

  - Make a workspace

  $ mkdir -p ~/omnirom
  $ cd ~/omnirom


  - Do repo init & sync

  $ repo init -u git://github.com/omnirom/android.git -b android-4.4


  - Create .repo/local_manifests/roomservice.xml with the following content:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <manifest>
    <remote name="oliver" fetch="https://github.com/OliverG96/" />
    <project name="android_device_samsung_serranoltexx" path="device/samsung/serranoltexx" revision="android-4.4" remote="oliver" />
    <project name="android_kernel_samsung_serranoltexx" path="kernel/samsung/serranoltexx" revision="android-4.4" remote="oliver" />
    <project name="android_vendor_samsung_serranoltexx" path="vendor/samsung/serranoltexx" revision="android-4.4" remote="oliver" />
  </manifest>

  $ repo sync

  - Setup environment

  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch omni_serranoltex-eng


  - Build OmniROM (4.4.4)

  $ export USE_CCACHE=1
  $ make -j4 bacon


